A=\frac{N!}{r! \cdot (N-r)!} \cdot p^r \cdot (1-p)^{N-r}
\log(A)\approx N\log(N)-r\log(r)-(N-r) \cdot \log(N-r)+r \cdot \log(p)/\log(2)+(N-r) \cdot \log(1-p)/\log(2)
B=\exp(-N \cdot (p \cdot \log_2(\frac{p}{r/N})+(1-p) \cdot \log_2(\frac{1-p}{1-r/N})))
\log(B)=-N \cdot (p \cdot \log_2(\frac{p}{r/N})+(1-p) \cdot \log_2(\frac{1-p}{1-r/N}))
